dip.judge.parser

Class JudgeImport

  • java.lang.Object
    • dip.judge.parser.JudgeImport

  • public class JudgeImport
extends java.lang.Object
    Imports text or reads a file, that is a Judge history file or listing. A World object is created from that file, if successful.
